data.description: This beautifully maintained Lennar home offers the perfect blend of modern elegance and functional design, promising a comfortable and enjoyable living experience. The seamless flow from the living room to the dining area and kitchen makes entertaining guests a delight. The three bedrooms plus a bonus room provide the perfect retreat, ensuring everyone has their own personal space to relax and recharge. The master suite is a true oasis, offering a tranquil escape with a well-appointed en-suite bath with large walk-in shower. Other great features include a Kinetico Water Softener, a Reme Halo LED air purification system, and a spacious three-car garage! Located in a great neighborhood, this home is close to all the amenities you desire, from shopping centers and restaurants to parks and recreational activities. Come experience the beauty of the Texas Hill Country while being able to experience the epitome of comfortable, elegant living in a fantastic community!
